if you're really hungry.

07:04.215 --> 07:07.176
(CUTLERY CLANKING)

07:24.986 --> 07:26.362
Don't mind her.

07:27.071 --> 07:29.321
She just needs time to process.

07:29.323 --> 07:30.199
It's been sudden.

07:31.367 --> 07:35.163
Like I need to tell you.
But I promise you nothing,

07:35.663 --> 07:38.583
nothing can make us happier
than you being home.

07:49.093 --> 07:52.180
(TENSE MUSIC)

08:27.965 --> 08:30.927
Good to see you out here.

08:34.388 --> 08:35.806
You went off the front door?

08:37.975 --> 08:40.394
You didn't talk to any
strangers, did you Michael?

08:41.895 --> 08:43.563
