going out front.

08:44.398 --> 08:45.900
You let me get the mail, okay?

08:47.568 --> 08:49.403
You know, I'm just
worried about you.

08:51.739 --> 08:52.657
What do you think?

09:04.961 --> 09:05.795
Michael?

09:09.090 --> 09:10.258
Michael?

