09:18.349 --> 09:19.600
Let's go inside.

09:27.316 --> 09:29.860
Well, here we are.

09:35.700 --> 09:36.951
Still not up for talking?

09:39.787 --> 09:40.663
Small steps, Donovan.

09:42.707 --> 09:43.499
Small steps.

09:48.504 --> 09:51.465
(SOFT PIANO MUSIC)

10:26.375 --> 10:27.376
So you're Donovan.

10:29.920 --> 10:31.420
I was.

10:31.422 --> 10:33.257
Does it bother
you that I'm here?

10:34.717 --> 10:35.716
I don't know.

10:35.718 --> 10:36.927
How are my parents?

10:39.680 --> 10:42.931
They're happy,
especially your dad.

10:42.933 --> 10:44.350
Good.

10:44.352 --> 10:45.519
Why are you here?

11:16.384 --> 11:19.553
Hey, how you doing?

11:22.473 --> 11:23.808
