watching him for family.

11:39.740 --> 11:41.450
(MUFFLED)
Good kid. Quiet.

11:42.159 --> 11:43.325
Lots of therapy.

11:43.327 --> 11:45.494
Okay, I just hope
I didn't startle him

11:45.496 --> 11:46.829
or anything like that, you know.

11:46.831 --> 11:48.082
Good seeing you.

11:56.132 --> 12:00.175
You know you're not
supposed to talk to strangers.

12:00.177 --> 12:01.637
He's not a stranger.

12:02.138 --> 12:05.681
Everyone outside of
this house is a stranger.

12:05.683 --> 12:07.683
No one can see you.

12:07.685 --> 12:09.101
No one can know
that you're here.

12:09.103 --> 12:10.438
Do you understand me?

12:14.024 --> 12:16.817
No garden or TV time for a week.

12:16.819 --> 12:19.280
Trust is earned in
this house, not given.

12:24.869 --> 12:27.538
(WATER RUNNING)

12:30.833 --> 12:33.377
(DRAMATIC MUSIC)

12:44.889 --> 12:46.307
You're gonna love this.

12:47.892 --> 12:49.310
You always did.

13:35.231 --> 13:38.067
(WAVES CRASHING)

13:42.029 --> 13:44.615
(MUSIC INTENSIFIES)

13:47.535 --> 13:48.744
Donovan!

14:04.218 --> 14:05.717
Donovan, what happened?

14:05.719 --> 14:06.470
Are you okay?

14:09.139 --> 14:09.932
What was...

