(EMOTIONAL PIANO MUSIC)

14:24.572 --> 14:30.325
Look, I know we can't just
pick up where we left off,

14:30.327 --> 14:31.245
I know that.

14:35.291 --> 14:37.501
And I'll never forget
the time we lost.

14:39.336 --> 14:40.671
